description.en:
Preparation of working samples:
- sewing stitches, connecting parts, fastening methods;
- skin with and without fur, skin of different animals;
- steel edges of the fur coat, fur skins, puffs, different fastening methods, hips and hems.

description.et:
Tööproovide valmistamine: 
- õmbluspisted, detailide ühendamised, kinnitusviisid;
- karvaga ja ilma karvata nahk, erinevate loomade nahk;
- kasukate teraskandid, liignahad, puhud, erinevad kinnitusviisid, puusad ja hännad.
